name: Susquehanna
ability: Sharply increases DMG dealt when another Black Ship is on the team.

additional_data.description: The spirit of one of the four black ships led by Commodore Perry when he reopened Japan  She tries to make a show of her strength to get what she wants, but Saratoga usually gets on her case about it and shuts her up. If Perry says anything, on the other hand, she'll hit and abuse him without a second thought. But it seems like he enjoys it...
additional_data.how_to_acquire:
◦ Limited Jewel Summon 19/10/16 to 09/11/16
◦ Trade at Exchange for 50 Mochi 06/11/16 - 09/11/16
additional_data.notes_and_trivia:
◦ Increases battle time limit by 20% during the "Meiji Monster on a Rampage" event.
◦ Summon rate increased until 19/10/16 to 09/11/16
◦ Susquehanna was one of the Black Ships used by Commodore Perry on his expeditions.

main: "Even a fraction of my strength will blow you to smithereens!"
summon: "Just follow my lead its for the best"
limit_break: "Now if I could just get a little bit taller..."
